Okay, I've got another list for you.

This time you're after {@LinkCreature:25#2011#ossugon warchiefs}, {@LinkCreature:25#2021#ossugon legates}, {@LinkCreature:25#2031#devan deathmasters}, {@LinkCreature:25#2041#Lokian snipers}, {@LinkCreature:25#2042#Lokian blood reapers}, {@LinkCreature:25#2061#devan vanguards}, {@LinkCreature:25#2071#dark deacons}, {@LinkCreature:25#2091#Lokian zealots}, and {@LinkCreature:25#2092#Lokian fanatics}.

And you'll be reporting to...Culetta, looks like. So go see her when you're done.
There's no dross in you! Well done!
Not dead, eh? Then why aren't you hunting cultists?
